![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/1622658779958-IFFK5OJ8BK4VJN09O93Q/180.jpg?format=original)

It's an X-Men Renaissance! After nearly a decade of aimless storytelling, the X-Men are in the hands of a master storyteller Jonathan Hickman and boy does he have plans for the World's Strangest Superheroes of All! Join us we marvel over the sweeping changes he's made to the franchise as it's laid out in his 2 part /12 issue introduction to HIS X-Men universe..**House of X** and **Powers of X**! By the way, while you slept...the world changed.

Please leave us a **_review_** on [**ITunes**](https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/major-issues-podcast/id1321720972) so we can grow our audience and grow as podcasters! Rate us where ever podcasts are found. Don't forget to check out our [merchandise](http://www.teepublic.com/user/comicbookclique)! All episodes of Major Issues are brought to you by [**ComicBookClique.com**](../episode/update/id/Comicbokclique.com), the home for the latest and greatest things to come to comic books and comic book media.  
  
